long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Gogi is a famous traveler, he lives in an unusual fairy-tale world, where there is something to see. Today, he goes to the valley, where carnivorous plants and stray mushroom grow monsters. Not everyone will dare to go on dangerous paths. Help the brave man to fulfill the plan and not become a dinner for the mutant's thorn.
